@section PAGE_GeometryPartOverview3 Use a DgnGeometryPart

The following code demonstrates how to reference a geometry part so that its geometry gets shared by (and at display-time, incorporated into) the GeometricElement.
@note Each time a geometry part is used, a placement (DPoint3d origin + YawPitchRollAngles rotation) or Transform must also be supplied.  This places the part relative to the element's local origin.

